    "For φ n ∈ C 1,2 ((0, T) × H n), h n ∈ C 1,2 ((0, T) × R), let ψ n (t, x):= φ n (t, x) + h n (t, |x|) be a test function in the sense of [52, Definition 3.32] and and let V n + ψ n have a global minimum at (t 0, x 0) ∈ (0, T) × H n.",
